description: Russia's president says the final decision would be in the hands of the Constitutional Court.
title: Putin paves way for another presidential term
title_page: Putin paves way for another presidential term - BBC News
maintext: Many people won't have a problem with that. If they don't actually like Mr Putin, they don't mind him too much either. Plenty of people view him as a strong leader who stands up to the West. Talk of there being no alternative is also commonplace.
